<h2 class="bold font-l">Gandrayda's Death</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Samus defeats the shapeshifter Gandrayda, and in her dying throes she transforms into various forms. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ShapeShifterSwanSong" class='trope-example-link'>Shapeshifter Swan Song</a></p>
